<p class="ayah 13-4" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَفِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قِطَعٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">are tracks</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّتَجَـٰوِرَٲتٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">neighboring,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجَنَّـٰتٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and gardens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْنَـٰبٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">grapevines</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَزَرْعٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and crops</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنَخِيلٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and date-palms</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صِنْوَانٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">trees (growing) from a single root</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَغَيْرُ صِنْوَانٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and trees not (growing) from a single root.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُسْقَىٰ</span><span class="