<p class="ayah 13-10" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَوَآءٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(It is) same (to Him)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[of you]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَسَرَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">conceals</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَوْلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the speech</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or (one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَهَرَ بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">publicizes it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[he]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُسْتَخْفِۭ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) hidden</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلَّيْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by night</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَسَارِبُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or goes freely</span></span><span cla