<p class="ayah 13-11" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">For him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُعَقِّبَـٰتٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) successive (Angels)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنۢ بَيْنِ يَدَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمِنْ خَلْفِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and behind him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَحْفَظُونَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who guard him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرِ ٱللَّهِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Command of Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(does) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُغَيِّرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">change</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا بِقَوْمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">