<p class="ayah 13-16" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّبُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth?"</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Allah."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَٱتَّخَذْتُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Have you then taken</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن دُونِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides Him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْلِيَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">protectors,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَمْلِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they have power</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَنفُسِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for themselves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) benefit</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضَرًّا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) harm?"</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَوِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">equal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَعْمَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the blind</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْبَصِيرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the seeing?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسْتَوِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">equal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظُّلُمَـٰتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the darkness[es]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلنُّورُ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the light?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَعَلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they attribute</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شُرَكَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">partners</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَخَلْقِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like His creation,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَشَـٰبَهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that seemed alike</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخَلْقُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the creation</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them?"</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rt