<p class="ayah 13-17" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنزَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He sends down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sky</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآءً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">water</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَسَالَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and flows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْدِيَةُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the valleys</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِقَدَرِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">according to their measure,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱحْتَمَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and carries</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّيْلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the torrent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زَبَدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a foam</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّابِيًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">rising.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمِمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And from what</span></span><span