<p class="ayah 13-35 selected" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ مَّثَلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">The example</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَنَّةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of Paradise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وُعِدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) promised</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُتَّقُونَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) the righteous,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">flows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْتِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">underneath it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rivers.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُكُلُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Its food</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَآئِمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) everlasting,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَظِلُّهَا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and its shad