<p class="ayah 13-37" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنزَلْنَـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have revealed it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حُكْمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to be) a judgment of authority</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَرَبِيًّا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) Arabic.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَئِنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّبَعْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you follow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْوَآءَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their desires</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعِلْمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the knowledge,</span></